
Feature: FloowDrive App Validation


Scenario: Home page Arrow button Validations
Given user is on Home Page
Then verify total number of journeys is displayed 
And verify total miles is displayed
And verify score card is displayed 
And verify backward arrow button is displayed and enabled
And verify forward arrow button is displayed and enabled

Scenero: Recording tab validations
Given user is on Home Page
Then verify Pause recording button is displayed and enabled

Scenero: Journeys tab validations
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks Journeys tab
Then all recorded journeys are displayed

Scenero: tabs switching validations
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks Journeys tab
and user clicks Home tab
Then Home page displayed

Scenero: tabs sliding validations
Given user is on Home Page
When user slides the page towards right side
Then verify journeys page is displayed
And user slides the page towards right side
And verify More options displayed
And user slides the page towards left side
And verify journeys page is displayed
And user slides the page towards left side
And verify Home page is displayed

Scenero: Home page left arrow button validations
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks left arrow button
Then Time of Day is displayed

Scenero: Home page left arrow button validations
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks left arrow button
And user clicks right arrow button
Then score is displayed

Scenero: Home page left arrow button validations
Given user is on Home Page
Then verify all the cards are available   // below data will be retrieved in the form of DataTable in StepDefinition to verify
|Score|
|Smooth Driving|
|Mobile Use|
|Speed|
|Fatigue|
|Time of Day|

Scenario Journeys Tab
Given user is on Home Page
When User clicked the Journeys tab
Then user view Journey recording information 

Scenario: More Options Validation
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks More tab
Then verify additional options displayed      // below data will be retrieved in the form of DataTable in StepDefinition to verify
|Preferences|
|FAQ|
|Terms and Conditions|
|About|
|Change Password|
|Contact Us|
|Tutorial|
|Optimisations|

Scenario: More - Preference Options Validation
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks More tab
And user clicks the Preferences option
Then verify the options can be selected   // below data will be retrieved in the form of DataTable in StepDefinition to verify
|Upload journeys over WIFI only|
|Battery conversion|
|Measurement units|
|Show confirmation when selecting a journey type|

Scenario: More - FAQS Options Validation
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks More tab
And user clicks the FAQS option
Then verify the options can be selected   // below data will be retrieved in the form of DataTable in StepDefinition to verify
|About the Floow Drive app|
|Use of the Floow Drive app|
|Journey Recording|
|Scoring|


Scenario: More- Terms and Conditions Option Validation
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks More tab
And user clicks the Terms and Conditions option
Then verify the terms and conditions message displayed

   
Scenario: More-About Option Validation
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks More tab
And user clicks the About option
Then verify the Log out and Third party licenses button displayed

Scenario: More-Change Password Option Validation
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks More tab
And user clicks the Change Password option
Then verify Current Password, New Password and Repeat new password fields are enabled and displayed
And verify Change it button displayed

Scenario: More-Contact Us Option Validation
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks More tab
And user clicks the Contact Us option
Then verify thefloow support email id is displayed within the clickable button

Scenario: More- Tutorial Option Validation
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks More tab
And user clicks Tutorial option
Then verify tutorial pages

Scenario: More - Optimizations Options Validation
Given user is on Home Page
When user clicks More tab
And user clicks the Optimizations option
